# Angular Todo App

Simple Todo List application built with Angular.

## 📌 Features

* Add new task
* Delete task
* Clean and simple UI

## 🛠 Technologies Used

* Angular
* TypeScript
* Bootstrap

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
npm install
ng serve
```

Then open:

```
http://localhost:4200
```

